sauce bar!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "we love to visit here every time we come to LA! this is the hot pot spot that made us fall in love with hot pot in the first place! they have the best snack and sauce bar!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "beyondtheveil", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113076921946666310300/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_p9DdJ_2olROinZB25G5J-mN3o31WUWL1Pcj4YCO3HIh2uZc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-09-12T18:59:41.033696346Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tzM1JsZHRhbGRWZEVoQmF6VnRkbFZYYkZSQlFXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tzM1JsZHRhbGRWZEVoQmF6VnRkbFZYYkZSQlFXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c32b62a9b035ab:0x39e74d88fc92ddb5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJqzWwqWIrw4ARtd2S_IhN5zk/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VPMk1fNzJzaE5TZ2NBEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Taste :4.3/5\nEnvironment: 4.3/5\nService：4.2/5\n\nLao Mao Tao Hot Pot in City of Industry isn’t for the mild-at-heart. This place is built for people who live for spice — and I mean, real spice. The kind that makes your lips tingle, your eyes water (a little), and your taste buds come alive.\n\nThe vibe is casual and energetic, with big groups gathered around bubbling pots full of red chili-laced broth. You pick your spice level, but fair warning: even the “medium” packs a punch. If you're a true spice lover, this place will absolutely test your limits — in the best way.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Taste :4.3/5\nEnvironment: 4.3/5\nService：4.2/5\n\nLao Mao Tao Hot Pot in City of Industry isn’t for the mild-at-heart. This place is built for people who live for spice — and I mean, real spice. The kind that makes your lips tingle, your eyes water (a little), and your taste buds come alive.\n\nThe vibe is casual and energetic, with big groups gathered around bubbling pots full of red chili-laced broth. You pick your spice level, but fair warning: even the “medium” packs a punch. If you're a true spice lover, this place will absolutely test your limits — in the best way.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Paprika Meow", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111635606610599291591/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXskclizzaADy-KSZ7es7UJT7HjvPayOn4lt0-Fc0onJPPd16EI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-05-14T20:07:51.552112Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VPMk1fNzJzaE5TZ2NBEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VPMk1fNzJzaE5TZ2NBEAE!2m1!1s0x80c32b62a9b035ab:0x39e74d88fc92ddb5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJqzWwqWIrw4ARtd2S_IhN5zk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOcFVVNURSalpOZGxWSE4waEhaa1ZNYmsxaFNGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "The food is genuinely delicious and clearly deserves the hype. Everything we ordered was great, and it’s easy to see why this place is always packed.\n\nThe wait time is long, which is expected for a spot this popular. What really took away from the experience, though, was the smoking situation while waiting to be seated. There were multiple people smoking in the waiting area, and the smoke lingered the entire time. By the time we sat down, the smell had already followed us.\n\nUnfortunately, the outdoor seating comes with a side of secondhand cigarette smoke, which made it hard to fully enjoy the meal. The staff were clearly overwhelmed due to how busy the restaurant was, so it didn’t feel realistic to expect them to step in.\n\nIt’s disappointing because the food itself is excellent, but the environment made the experience far less enjoyable than it should have been.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The food is genuinely delicious and clearly deserves the hype. Everything we ordered was great, and it’s easy to see why this place is always packed.\n\nThe wait time is long, which is expected for a spot this popular. What really took away from the experience, though, was the smoking situation while waiting to be seated. There were multiple people smoking in the waiting area, and the smoke lingered the entire time. By the time we sat down, the smell had already followed us.\n\nUnfortunately, the outdoor seating comes with a side of secondhand cigarette smoke, which made it hard to fully enjoy the meal. The staff were clearly overwhelmed due to how busy the restaurant was, so it didn’t feel realistic to expect them to step in.\n\nIt’s disappointing because the food itself is excellent, but the environment made the experience far less enjoyable than it should have been.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ken Ta", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117070025340300004366/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqapOjqgvalzbXaxq5gb-CP385s0oPbL9GFSkag7NFejFBxw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-07T02:48:55.153824604Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOcFVVNURSalpOZGxWSE4waEhaa1ZNYmsxaFNGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOcFVVNURSalpOZGxWSE4waEhaa1ZNYmsxaFNGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c32b62a9b035ab:0x39e74d88fc92ddb5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJqzWwqWIrw4ARtd2S_IhN5zk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkWk1XbFlVeTFOU0hwUWVGVXlWMFJTYXpKVVIyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Not even worth it...I went to have lunch with my mom for $24.99 AYCE. $24.99 for 2 round and only have 5 choices of meat (only meat) with the maximum of 4 order. It turned out the soup base and snack bar are separate. The snack bar has the hotpot sauce. The soup base are about $18-20. The snack bar are about $3.95 per person. The vegetable and tofu are not part of $24.99. Usually, the hotpot sauce are free in other restaurant. Is it really worth it? Not for me. Will I come back? HELL NO. If I want to eat hotpot especially AYCE hotpot, I will go to other restaurant that dont charge for hotpot sauce and the soup base are part of the $24.95. I highly recommend to go another restaurant for an actual AYCE hotpot like Happy Lamb, and Momo Paradise, etc. The service was horrible especially the male employees. When we were eating here, we always avoided the male employee.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Not even worth it...I went to have lunch with my mom for $24.99 AYCE. $24.99 for 2 round and only have 5 choices of meat (only meat) with the maximum of 4 order. It turned out the soup base and snack bar are separate. The snack bar has the hotpot sauce. The soup base are about $18-20. The snack bar are about $3.95 per person. The vegetable and tofu are not part of $24.99. Usually, the hotpot sauce are free in other restaurant. Is it really worth it? Not for me. Will I come back? HELL NO. If I want to eat hotpot especially AYCE hotpot, I will go to other restaurant that dont charge for hotpot sauce and the soup base are part of the $24.95. I highly recommend to go another restaurant for an actual AYCE hotpot like Happy Lamb, and Momo Paradise, etc. The service was horrible especially the male employees. When we were eating here, we always avoided the male employee.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Timothy", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110938630214736947674/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1aNJ1KfB1VU1APFh4EjQdzf1ytvzCSgUISKZTbHZsXRiRSq2K=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-23T03:25:30.130007355Z", "flagCo